    "instruction": "Load metric.csv, trace.csv, log.csv, and error_logs.csv. For each file, return a compact summary containing: total row count; the minimum and maximum timestamp (as integers); up to 20 distinct cmdb_id values with their counts (most frequent first); and up to 20 distinct KPI/trace/log names (kpi_name for metric.csv, trace_name for trace.csv, log_name for log.csv, and none for error_logs.csv) with their counts (most frequent first). Do not print full rows. Keep each list limited to top 20 entries."
